    "They also filled out the ChatGPT Instructional Use Intention Scale again.",
    "Following the scale completion, six students were randomly selected for semi-structured interviews regarding their experiences using ChatGPT and their instructional use intentions.",
    "After the interviews, the project entered the effectiveness evaluation phase.",
    "Research personnel assessed 50 project outcomes based on evaluation criteria.",
    "The criteria included coordinates, legends, colors, overall coherence, numerical indicators, titles, and stacking patterns, comprising seven observation points."
